<h2>Password Changed Successfully</h2>

<p>Hi {{name}},</p>

<div class="success-box">
  <p><strong>✅ Your password has been changed successfully</strong></p>
</div>

<p>This email confirms that your password was changed on:</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>📅 Date:</strong> {{formatDate timestamp}}</p>
  <p><strong>🌍 IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</p>
  <p><strong>🖥️ Device:</strong> {{device}}</p>
</div>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p><strong>⚠️ Didn't change your password?</strong></p>
  <p>If you didn't make this change, your account may be compromised. Please contact support immediately:</p>
  <a href="{{supportUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Support</a>
</div>

<p>For your security, all active sessions have been logged out. You'll need to log in again with your new password.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Coffee App Team</p>
